data.description: This charming 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home is ready for its new owners! Boasting brick on all four sides, a large backyard, mature trees, and an inviting entry courtyard. Just under 1500 square feet with granite counters throughout, split bedrooms, and a large living area.  The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, a breakfast bar, and pantry.  Recently added window screens throughout. Do not hesitate, schedule your tours today.
